headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Celebrate 4/20 in GTA Online
content:
Boost your stoner cred by logging in to GTA Online this week to receive the Sprunk Chute Bag and Pastel Green Smoking Jacket.

Have an out-of-body experience in Short Trips and get Weed Farm Bonuses, including doubled production speeds at Weed Farms.

Plus, those looking to join the green rush can get 30% off Weed Farm locations and upgrades.
